flowRoot.flowPara: Plays On : Master System, Master System II and Mega Drive/Genesis With Master System/Power Base Converter
The purpose of the game is to make your rocket land safely on landing areas (horizontal with red dots) without using all your gaz.
- press 1 to start and pass texts
- press 2 when you lost to restart from the first level (pressing 1 will restart the level you lost in with full gaz)
- press down to decrease vertical speed
- press left/right to change horizontal speed
Warning: acceleration is in the opposite direction of the direction you press!
